---
/* You can add logic here later, like fetching data */
---
<section class="relative py-20 bg-tcm-stone overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <span class="text-tcm-gold font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">
                Traditionell Kinesisk Medicin
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-tcm-green mt-4 mb-6">
                Naturlig hälsa i <span class="text-stone-800">Nyköping & Gnesta</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Vi hjälper dig med akupunktur, koppning och örtmedicin för en balanserad vardag.
                Boka din behandling i våra kliniker i Sörmland.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="#boka"
                    class="bg-tcm-green text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-opacity-90 transition">
                    Boka Tid
                </a>
                <a href="/behandlingar"
                    class="border border-tcm-green text-tcm-green px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-tcm-green hover:text-white transition">
                    Våra Behandlingar
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>